        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> A creature within 30 feet has the frightened condition.</p><hr /><p>You snarl ferociously at a creature within 30 feet, menacing them with bared teeth. Increase the value of the frightened condition by 1 (maximum 3). The target then becomes temporarily immune to your Menacing Snarl for 24 hours.</p>\n<p>As long as the target is frightened, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to melee Strikes against that creature, and damage dealt to the creature by your melee Strikes deals an additional @Damage[1[mental]] damage per damage die.</p>"
